        <section>
            <h2>8.1 Your privacy rights.</h2>
            <p>In relation to our processing of your personal data, you may have the below privacy rights.
            Right to withdraw consent. In so far as our processing of your data is based on your consent, you have the
            right to withdraw your consent at any time via our contact details stated below. Withdrawal of consent does
