            <p>Right to complaint. In addition to the above-mentioned rights, you may have the right to lodge a complaint
            with a supervisory authority, in particular in the country of your habitual residence, place of work or
            where an alleged infringement took place. However, we would appreciate the chance to deal with your concerns
            before you approach them, so please contact us beforehand.</p>

